TITLE: Common Redis Command Patterns for Rueidis in Go
DESCRIPTION: This set of examples illustrates various common Redis commands and how to parse their results using the Rueidis library in Go. It covers commands like GET, MGET, SET, INCR, HGET, and more. Each command is demonstrated with the appropriate parsing function that matches the expected type of response (e.g., ToString, AsInt64, ToArray).
SOURCE: https://github.com/inngest/inngest/blob/main/vendor/github.com/redis/rueidis/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_15

LANGUAGE: golang
