TITLE: Processing Amazon Connect Events Using AWS Lambda in Go
DESCRIPTION: This Go code implements an AWS Lambda function that receives Amazon Connect events, logs event details to CloudWatch, and returns a response. It extracts the ContactID from the event, prints all parameters received, and returns a success response with a new attribute.
