TITLE: Alternative PubSub Hooks - golang
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to utilize `SetPubSubHooks()` to define hooks for channel subscription management. It allows the client to handle messages and manage disconnections asynchronously. The provided `wait` channel helps detect disconnection reasons after subscription commands.
