TITLE: Channel Sender Function in Go with GopherLua
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates sending values through channels using GopherLua's channel API and Go channel operations
SOURCE: https://github.com/inngest/inngest/blob/main/vendor/github.com/yuin/gopher-lua/README.rst#2025-04-22_snippet_21

