TITLE: Implementing petname in Python
DESCRIPTION: A Python script that uses the petname library to generate pet names. It sets up command-line arguments for customizing the output, similar to the Go version.
SOURCE: https://github.com/inngest/inngest/blob/main/vendor/github.com/dustinkirkland/golang-petname/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

